* Iron Raptor looked around the smaller of the two Conference Rooms, 
wondering just what Prowl would be up to right about now.
She sighed and walked out of the small room, just in time to see Hot Rod 
walk into the room, another bot following him into the room.
She looked at him, wondering just what it was now that she had to tend to.
And, also wondering just when Firearm was going to get down to work and 
bring both Tavatron anf Dinobot back.
But then she focused on Hot Rod again.*

" Can I help you?"
